OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105894
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,FAn exceptionally rare fragment of a
OL,8,Fhandwritten letter and signature from
OL,9,Fpioneering fossil collector Mary
OL,10,FAnning has revealed she got sick of
OL,11,Fher hobby.
OL,13,FThe part of the letter which has
OL,14,Fsurvived is signed by Mary and in it
OL,15,Fshe reveals that she is "worn out"
OL,16,Fadding "the name of fossils makes me
OL,17,Fsick".
OL,26,@wD@YOUwD@bO]xD@HOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
