FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105894
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,FAlthough the letter is short it gives
OL,8,Fan intimate glimpse into Mary's
OL,9,Finnermost thoughts of which very
OL,10,Flittle is known.
OL,12,FMary Anning was born in Lyme Regis in
OL,13,F1799 to a poor working-class family.
OL,15,FShe overcame the societal pressures of
OL,16,Fclass and sex to be a groundbreaking
OL,17,Ffemale palaeontologist in the early
OL,18,Fdays of the discipline.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105894
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,FIn 2010 she was voted as one of the
OL,8,Ften most influential women in British
OL,9,Fscience history by the Royal Society.
OL,11,FIn 2022, as a result of a crowdfunding
OL,12,Fcampaign, a new public statue of Mary
OL,13,FAnning was unveiled on the Lyme Regis
OL,14,Fseafront.
OL,16,FThe letter, which is being sold by
OL,17,Fauctioneers Bonhams, is only the
OL,18,Fsecond one to come up for sale and an
OL,19,Fappeal has been launched to secure it
OL,20,Ffor Lyme Regis Philpot Museum.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
