OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105894
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,FThere are six lines, including the
OL,8,Fwords lamenting that she was "...worn
OL,9,Fout after you saw me that I almost
OL,10,Fwish'd that I might never see a Lady
OL,11,Fagain and the name of fossils makes me
OL,12,Fsick with its concominants (sic)..."
OL,14,FIt is signed "Gratefully yours Mary
OL,15,FAnning" with note beneath in another
OL,16,Fnineteenth-century hand "The
OL,17,Fcelebrated Lyme Regis geologist"
OL,19,FA campaign to buy the letter is led by
OL,20,Fthe Friends of Lyme Regis Museum.
OL,26,@tD@\pmtD@`pn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
