OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105895
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,FThe charity which fundraised for Mary
OL,8,FAnning's statue in Lyme Regis, Visible
OL,9,FWomen, posted on social media about
OL,10,Fthe importance of the letter.
OL,12,FIt reads: "This is her voice. Six
OL,13,Flines. A signature. And a moment of
OL,14,Fraw honesty from one of the most
OL,15,Fimportant scientific minds this
OL,16,Fcountry has ever produced:
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105895
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,F"This is a woman who changed science
OL,8,Fforever along the Jurassic Coast. A
OL,9,Fworking-class woman. Self-taught.
OL,10,FOperating in a world that excluded her
OL,11,Fat every level, including being shut
OL,12,Fout of the Geological Society of
OL,13,FLondon.
OL,15,F"Her discoveries built reputations for
OL,16,Fmen who often didn't credit her. She
OL,17,Fsupplied the specimens, the knowledge,
OL,18,Fthe intellectual labour, and still had
OL,19,Fto fight to be seen.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105895
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,F"And here, in these six surviving
OL,8,Flines, you feel the cost of that.
OL,9,FExhaustion. Frustration. A sharp,
OL,10,Falmost biting wit. A woman worn down
OL,11,Fby the very field she revolutionised.
OL,13,F"Manuscripts from Mary Anning are
OL,14,Fexceptionally rare. Only two full
OL,15,Fletters are known to exist. It should
OL,16,Fbe in Lyme Regis. Not in a private
OL,17,Fcollection. Not disappearing from
OL,18,Fpublic view."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
