PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774105895
OL,3,CRare glimpse into life of famous
OL,4,Cfossil-finder reveals she got sick of
OL,5,Cher hobby
OL,7,FLyme Regis Museum says if it can buy
OL,8,Fthe letter it will go on display so
OL,9,Fpeople can see it on the site of her
OL,10,Fformer home overlooking the Jurassic
OL,11,FCoast.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
